title: RECENTLY BUILT luxury condo, in the vibrant Marina District, FULLY FUR
posting_body: RECENTLY BUILT 28-unit LUXURY, boutique condo, 4-story building: First new construction in the Marina District in decades.

State of the art Concrete and Steel building celebrates great architecture and aesthetics and provides the ultimate in acoustic insulation (wouldn’t it be nice not to hear the neighbor’s walking around?).
This is the only 4 story building in SF which is concrete and steel.
And it is one of the few sites NOT on landfill in the Marina District
